@startuml
actor Client
participant "PlayerController\n(DTO Layer)" as PlayerController
participant "PlayerService\n(Business Logic)" as PlayerService
participant "PlayerRepository\n(Entity Layer)" as PlayerRepository
database DB

Client -> PlayerController : POST /players\nplayerDTO
note right of PlayerController: Validación automática del DTO\n(@Valid, @NotNull, etc.)

PlayerController -> PlayerService : createPlayer(playerDTO)
note right of PlayerService: Aplica lógica de negocio:\n- Mapea DTO -> Entity\n- Verifica club existente\n- Reglas de negocio (ej.: número de dorsal único)

PlayerService -> PlayerRepository : save(player)
PlayerRepository -> DB : INSERT INTO player ...
DB --> PlayerRepository : OK / generated id
PlayerRepository --> PlayerService : Player entity

PlayerService --> PlayerController : PlayerDTO
PlayerController --> Client : 201 Created\nplayerDTO
@enduml
